[%cal Gf1e1,Gf3e5] White's plan is to bring one of his rooks to e1 and to
install the knight on e5, with annoying pressure on Black's camp.} h6 13. Bh4
Bxf3 $1 {Avoiding the aforementioned plan by very concrete means.} 14. Qxf3 {
